data.title: Secretary Kerry, French Foreign Minister Fabius Address Reporters Following Meeting in Paris
data.meta_description: U.S. Secretary of State John Kerry stands with French Foreign Minister Laurent Fabius as the two address reporters after a working lunch and bilateral meeting at the Quai d'Orsay - the French Foreign Ministry - in Paris, France, on November 5, 2014. [State Department photo/ Public Domain]
